high_descs: To to the end of the island across from the fridge.
Pick up the sharp knife in between the other two.
Slice the tomato on the island.
Go to the end of the island with the shadow on it.
Set the knife down on the plate on the island.
Go back to the right side of the island.
Pick up a slice of tomato on the island.
Go to the end of the island with the shadow.
Set the tomato slice on the plate.
Pick up the plate with tomato and knife on it.
Go to the fridge on the right.
Put the items in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a tomato slice and knife on it into the fridge.

high_descs: Walk forward and around to the far side of the kitchen island then turn back to face it
Pick up the knife just right of the tomato from the kitchen island
Use the knife to slice the tomato on the kitchen island
Turn left and walk around to the side of the kitchen island
Put the knife down on the plate on the kitchen island
Turn right and walk back around to the side of the kitchen island opposite the sink
Pick up a slice of tomato from the kitchen island
Turn left and walk back over to the side of the kitchen island
Put the tomato slice on the plate on the kitchen island
Pick up the plate from the kitchen island
Turn right and walk around the kitchen island to the fridge
Put the plate into the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put the plate with knife and tomato slice in the fridge

high_descs: Turn left and take a step.  Turn right and walk to the trash can.  At the trash can, turn left and walk to the middle of the table.
Pick up the middle knife to the closest to the salt.
Slice the tomato in the middle of the table.
Carrying the knife, turn left and walk to the the trash can, at the trash can turn right and walk to the edge of the table.   Face the table.
Put the knife down on the plate next to the lettuce.
Turn right and walk to the trash can.  At the trash can, turn left and walk to the middle of the table.  Face the table.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Carrying the tomato slice, turn left and walk to the the trash can, at the trash can turn right and walk to the edge of the table.   Face the table.
Put the tomato down on the plate to the left of the knife.
Pick up the plate with the tomato slice and knife.

Carry the plate, turn right and walk to the trash can.  At the trash can, turn left and walk to the wall on the other side of the room.  At the wall, turn right and face the refrigerator.  Walk toward the refrigerator.
Open both of the refrigerator doors.  Put the plate down to the right of the glass in the refrigerator.  Close both doors..
anns.task_desc: Slice a tomato and cool in refrigerator.
